WaitFrame (script event)
========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type [Thread\_(scripting).html idThread], accessible via [Scripting\_basics.html\#sys sys] identifier.

Description
-----------

Suspends execution of current [Thread\_(scripting).html thread] for one game frame.

Usage
-----

*[Data\_types.html\#void void]* waitFrame()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

